pages(/meta/): replace visualstudio.com badge with shields.io one
Summary: Re-implements D439. `visualstudio.com` injects cookies, which is not desirable. Using `data:` uri because shields.io's upstream logo provider is [removing them](https://github.com/simple-icons/simple-icons/pull/10019).
Signed-off-by: Yongmin Hong <revi@omglol.email>
Test Plan: `npm cleanbuild`, `npm run lighthouse` and verify no third party cookie warning.
Reviewers: O2 Coders, O1 revi & automations, revi
Reviewed By: O2 Coders, O1 revi & automations, revi
Differential Revision: https://issuetracker.revi.xyz/D500
